LAHORE, Nov 13 (APP): Punjab Chief Minister Sardar Usman Buzdar condoled the death of Chief Justice Peshawar High Court Justice Waqar Ahmad Seth.
In a message on Friday, the chief minister extended sympathies to the bereaved family and prayed that may Allah Almighty rest the departed soul in peace.
